      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PHANTOM CARAT (5) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (22.96) last time in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Has ability and looks hard to stop. TOBY KEEPING (2) was prominent throughout when an impressive winner two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 12 lengths at Angle Park (31.06). Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Expected to give a good account. CRITICAL MASS (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 2.25 lengths (17.38) at this track. Has placed a couple of times at this track. Worth another chance. GRAPEFRUIT WILMA (4) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
